<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA93">
<l>vayiṟaḻala vāḷuruvi vantāṉai yañca</l>
<l>veyiṟilaka vāymaṭutta teṉṉī – poṟiyukirāṟ</l>
<l>pūvaṭivai yīṭaḻitta poṉṉāḻik kaiyāniṉ</l>
<l>cēvaṭimē līṭaḻiyac ceṟṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you suck [his blood] with [your] mouth, so that [your] teeth shone terrifyingly,</l>
<l>him who had come in the form of light , so that [his] belly burned,</l>
<l>o you with the golden discus in [your] hand that degraded [its] flower form by tainted nails,</l>
<l>destroying [him] so that he lost [his] strength on your red feet?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
